The pausebutton click listener is incorrect

Current Code
{code}
pauseButton.addEventListener('click', function() {
    streamer.pause();
    if (streamer.paused) {
        pauseButton.title = 'Unpause Streaming';
    }
    else {
        pauseButton.title = 'Pause Streaming';
    }
});
{code}

Correct Code
{code}
pauseButton.addEventListener('click', function() {
    if (pauseButton.title == 'Pause Streaming') {
        streamer.pause();
        pauseButton.title = 'Unpause Streaming';
    }
    else {
        streamer.start();
        pauseButton.title = 'Pause Streaming';
    }
});
{code}


The error on the standalone app is due to the fact that you are passing in an empty url to the audio player proxy.
Remove the clearOnEdit:true property from the textField and everything should be fine.
